WEBVTT

1
00:00:03.166 --> 00:00:03.966
Come on.

2
00:00:17.766 --> 00:00:18.933
Don't you want to know

3
00:00:18.933 --> 00:00:20.833
Who is Shanshan's biological mother?

4
00:00:24.500 --> 00:00:25.966
When you and I were married for one night

5
00:00:25.966 --> 00:00:28.200
I'd rather you want a mother and a child

6
00:00:28.500 --> 00:00:30.700
Took your child and went into the in-law's house

7
00:00:31.133 --> 00:00:34.233
The real mistress of my house should have been you

8
00:00:34.666 --> 00:00:36.666
I want to tell me this now

9
00:00:36.700 --> 00:00:37.200
Do you know

10
00:00:37.200 --> 00:00:39.700
How desperate I felt when I walked in

11
00:00:41.100 --> 00:00:43.200
Nuannuan, I promise you

12
00:00:43.700 --> 00:00:45.466
I owe you five years of these years

13
00:00:45.700 --> 00:00:48.300
I'll help you take it back from him the same way

